	  <p>Our hottest new transmission fix of the year – the Sonnax <a href="http://www.sonnax.com/product-lines/high-performance-transmission/parts/1338">SmartShell&trade;</a> – is featured in our latest edition of the Transmission Report. This in-depth tech article covers the root-cause of problems with the GM 4L60 sun gear shell and the smarter, Sonnax solution that tackles them all. Also featured: 4L60 durability upgrades, our new transmission catalog and Jatco/Nissan CVT fixes. If you didn't receive this newsletter, click here to request a copy (U.S. only) or read the latest newsletter online.</p>
        
